A4.text: The Brothers Karamazov is the eighth and final novel by Russian author Fyodor Dostoevsky.

A5.text: Dostoevsky spent nearly two years writing The Brothers Karamazov, which was published as a serial in The Russian Messenger from January 1879 to November 1880.
